statements: SELECT user_id, username, user_email, behavior_type, timestamp FROM user_behavior_data;
SELECT * FROM user_behavior_data WHERE user_id = 100;
SELECT username, behavior_type FROM user_behavior_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, user_email FROM user_behavior_data WHERE behavior_type = 'click' LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, username FROM user_behavior_data WHERE username LIKE '%john%' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM user_behavior_data WHERE behavior_type = 'login' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT user_id, username FROM user_behavior_data WHERE behavior_type = 'purchase'
SELECT * FROM user_behavior_data WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND behavior_type IN ('login', 'purchase') ORDER BY timestamp
SELECT username, behavior_type FROM user_behavior_data WHERE user_id IN (100, 200, 300) ORDER BY user_id DESC
SELECT COUNT(user_id) AS user_count, behavior_type FROM user_behavior_data GROUP BY behavior_type HAVING user_count > 5
SELECT * FROM user_behavior_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, behavior_type FROM user_behavior_data WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT behavior_type, location FROM user_behavior_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT theme, language, auto_play FROM user_preferences WHERE notification_enabled = TRUE;
SELECT user_id, location, duration FROM user_behavior_data WHERE behavior_type = 'click' AND duration > 10 ORDER BY timestamp;
SELECT * FROM user_behavior_data WHERE behavior_type = 'click' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT user_id, location, duration FROM user_behavior_data WHERE user_id = 1001 AND location LIKE '%home%'
SELECT user_id, theme, language FROM user_preferences WHERE language = 'English' AND notification_enabled = TRUE ORDER BY user_id ASC
SELECT behavior_type, count(*) AS frequency FROM user_behavior_data GROUP BY behavior_type ORDER BY frequency DESC
SELECT u.user_id, u.theme, u.language, p.auto_play FROM user_preferences p INNER JOIN user_behavior_data u ON u.user_id = p.user_id WHERE u.duration > 60 AND p.theme = 'Light' ORDER BY u.user_id ASC

SELECT user_profiles.*, user_actions.action_type, user_actions.timestamp FROM user_profiles JOIN user_actions ON user_profiles.user_id = user_actions.user_id WHERE user_actions.action_type = 'login' ORDER BY user_actions.timestamp DESC;

SELECT user_id, preference_name, preference_value FROM user_profiles JOIN user_preferences ON user_profiles.user_id = user_preferences.user_id WHERE preference_name IN ('theme', 'notifications') AND user_profiles.created_at >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT user_profiles.username, user_actions.action_type, user_preferences.preference_value FROM user_profiles LEFT JOIN user_actions ON user_profiles.user_id = user_actions.user_id LEFT JOIN user_preferences ON user_profiles.user_id = user_preferences.user_id WHERE user_preferences.preference_name IS NULL OR user_profiles.username LIKE '%admin%';
